<div class=3D"PageInfo">
<p>
Here is our feet and inches to cm conversion calculator
which will help you convert from feet and inches into cm.
</p>
<p>
The converter will also show you the formula you need to convert between un=
its.
</p>
<p class=3D"BoldCt">How It Works...</p>
<p>Step 1) Type in the length in feet and inches.</p>
<p>Step 2) (Optional) - choose what accuracy you want your answer - the def=
ault is 1 decimal place.</p>
<p>Step 3) Click the Convert button and the answer will be displayed.</p>
<br>
