<h3 class=3D"SubHeading">How to convert from feet and inches into cm</h3>
<div class=3D"CalloutBox">
<p class=3D"BoldCt">How to convert from feet and inches to cm</p>
<p>Step 1) Convert the feet into inches.</p>
<p>1 foot =3D 12 inches, so we need to multiply the amount of feet by 12.</=
p>
<p>Step 2) Find the total number of inches by adding the number from Step 1=
) to the number of inches.</p>
<p>Step 3) Multiply this number by 2.54 (because 1 inch =3D 2.54 cm)</p>
</div><div id=3D"AdThrive_Content_3_tablet" class=3D"adthrive-ad adthrive-s=
ticky-container adthrive-content adthrive-content-3 adthrive-ad-cls"></div>
<h3 class=3D"ExampleSubHeading">Examples</h3>
<div class=3D"CalloutBox">
<p class=3D"ExampleText">1) Convert 4 foot 8 inches into cm.</p>
<p>Step 1) We need to convert 4 foot into inches.</p>
<p>4 x 12 =3D 48 inches</p>
<p>Step 2) We need to find the total number of inches.</p>
<p>48 + 8 =3D 56 inches</p>
<p>Step 3) We need to convert this to cm by multiplying by 2.54</p>
<p>56 x 2.54 =3D 142.24 cm</p>
<p class=3D"ExampleText">So 4 foot 8 inches =3D 142.2cm (to 1dp).</p>
<br><br>
<p class=3D"ExampleText">2) Convert 3 foot 5 inches to cm.</p>
<p>Step 1) Convert the feet to inches.</p>
<p>3 x 12 =3D 36 inches</p>
<p>Step 2) Find the total number of inches.</p>
<p>36 + 5 =3D 41 inches</p>
<p>Step 3) Convert this to cm by multiplying by 2.54</p>
<p>41 x 2.54 =3D 104.14 cm</p>
<p class=3D"ExampleText">So 3 foot 5 inches =3D 104.14 cm.</p>
</div><div id=3D"AdThrive_Content_4_tablet" class=3D"adthrive-ad adthrive-s=
ticky-container adthrive-content adthrive-content-4 adthrive-ad-cls"></div>
<p class=3D"SubHeading">Common Conversions Facts feet and inches to cm</p>
<div class=3D"PageInfo">
<p>Here are some a few quick simple conversion facts from feet to inches.</=
p>
<ul>
<li>1 foot =3D 12 inches =3D 30.48 cm</li>
<li>2 feet =3D 24 inches =3D 60.96 cm</li>
<li>3 feet =3D 36 inches =3D 91.44 cm</li>
<li>4 feet =3D 48 inches =3D 121.92 cm</li>
<li>5 feet =3D 60 inches =3D 152.4 cm</li>
<li>6 feet =3D 72 inches =3D 182.88</li>
<li>7 feet =3D 84 inches =3D 213.36 cm</li>
<li>10 feet =3D 120 inches =3D 304.8 cm</li>
<li>100 feet =3D 1200 inches =3D 3048 cm</li>
</ul>
<p>Here are some a few quick simple conversion facts from inches to cm.</p>
<ul>
<li>1 in =3D 2.54 cm</li>
<li>2 in =3D 5.08 cm</li>
<li>10 in =3D 25.4 cm</li>
<li>100 in =3D 254 cm</li>
<li>1000 in =3D 2,540 cm</li>
</ul>
</div>
